{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":801,"text":"What if I told you\nthere was a new technology"},{"time":4700,"text":"that, when placed in the hands\nof doctors and nurses,"},{"time":9292,"text":"improved outcomes for children\nand adults, patients of all ages;"},{"time":15491,"text":"reduced pain and suffering,"},{"time":18058,"text":"reduced time in the operating rooms,"},{"time":21271,"text":"reduced anesthetic times,"},{"time":24148,"text":"had the ultimate dose-response curve"},{"time":26070,"text":"that the more you did it,"},{"time":27840,"text":"the better it benefitted patients?"},{"time":31340,"text":"Here's a kicker: it has no side effects,"},{"time":33766,"text":"and it's available no matter\nwhere care is delivered."},{"time":37505,"text":"I can tell you as an ICU doctor\nat Boston Children's Hospital,"},{"time":40971,"text":"this would be a game changer for me."},{"time":43302,"text":"That technology is lifelike rehearsal."},{"time":48713,"text":"This lifelike rehearsal is being delivered\nthrough medical simulation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":53891,"text":"I thought I would start with a case,"},{"time":57916,"text":"just to really describe\nthe challenge ahead,"},{"time":60650,"text":"and why this technology is not just\ngoing to improve health care"},{"time":64045,"text":"but why it's critical to health care."},{"time":67568,"text":"This is a child that's born, young girl."},{"time":70465,"text":"\"Day of life zero,\" we call it,"},{"time":72249,"text":"the first day of life,\njust born into the world."},{"time":74572,"text":"And just as she's being born,"},{"time":75987,"text":"we notice very quickly\nthat she is deteriorating."},{"time":78939,"text":"Her heart rate is going up,\nher blood pressure is going down,"},{"time":81876,"text":"she's breathing very, very fast."},{"time":84277,"text":"And the reason for this\nis displayed in this chest X-ray."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89203,"text":"That's called a babygram,"},{"time":90538,"text":"a full X-ray of a child's body,\na little infant's body."},{"time":93836,"text":"As you look on the top side of this,"},{"time":95766,"text":"that's where the heart and lungs\nare supposed to be."},{"time":98273,"text":"As you look at the bottom end,\nthat's where the abdomen is,"},{"time":101074,"text":"and that's where the intestines\nare supposed to be."},{"time":103520,"text":"And you can see how\nthere's sort of that translucent area"},{"time":106273,"text":"that made its way up into the right side\nof this child's chest."},{"time":109468,"text":"And those are the intestines --\nin the wrong place."},{"time":113500,"text":"As a result, they're pushing on the lungs"},{"time":115694,"text":"and making it very difficult\nfor this poor baby to breathe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":119218,"text":"The fix for this problem"},{"time":120735,"text":"is to take this child immediately\nto the operating room,"},{"time":123413,"text":"bring those intestines\nback into the abdomen,"},{"time":125568,"text":"let the lungs expand"},{"time":127007,"text":"and allow this child to breathe again."},{"time":129487,"text":"But before she can go\nto the operating room,"},{"time":131570,"text":"she must get whisked away\nto the ICU, where I work."},{"time":134886,"text":"I work with surgical teams."},{"time":136778,"text":"We gather around her,"},{"time":138104,"text":"and we place this child\non heart-lung bypass."},{"time":143596,"text":"We put her to sleep,"},{"time":145241,"text":"we make a tiny\nlittle incision in the neck,"},{"time":147861,"text":"we place catheters into the major\nvessels of the neck --"},{"time":151023,"text":"and I can tell you that these vessels\nare about the size of a pen,"},{"time":154741,"text":"the tip of a pen --"},{"time":156670,"text":"and then we have blood\ndrawn from the body,"},{"time":158778,"text":"we bring it through a machine,\nit gets oxygenated,"},{"time":161210,"text":"and it goes back into the body."},{"time":163086,"text":"We save her life,"},{"time":164686,"text":"and get her safely to the operating room."}]},{"cues":[{"time":169050,"text":"Here's the problem:"},{"time":171872,"text":"these disorders --"},{"time":173469,"text":"what is known is congenital\ndiaphragmatic hernia --"},{"time":176782,"text":"this hole in the diaphragm that has\nallowed these intestines to sneak up --"},{"time":180402,"text":"these disorders are rare."},{"time":183293,"text":"Even in the best hands in the world,"},{"time":187142,"text":"there is still a challenge\nto get the volume --"},{"time":190676,"text":"the natural volume of these patients --"},{"time":192598,"text":"in order to get our expertise\ncurve at 100 percent."},{"time":195144,"text":"They just don't present that often."},{"time":198729,"text":"So how do you make the rare common?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":204101,"text":"Here's the other problem:"},{"time":206359,"text":"in the health care system\nthat I trained for over 20 years,"},{"time":210984,"text":"what currently exists,"},{"time":212193,"text":"the model of training is called\nthe apprenticeship model."},{"time":215161,"text":"It's been around for centuries."},{"time":217100,"text":"It's based on this idea that you see\na surgery maybe once,"},{"time":221072,"text":"maybe several times,"},{"time":222624,"text":"you then go do that surgery,"},{"time":225438,"text":"and then ultimately you teach\nthat surgery to the next generation."},{"time":230442,"text":"And implicit in this model --"},{"time":233216,"text":"I don't need to tell you this --"},{"time":235414,"text":"is that we practice on the very patients\nthat we are delivering care to."},{"time":242303,"text":"That's a problem."},{"time":247276,"text":"I think there's a better approach."},{"time":249497,"text":"Medicine may very well be the last\nhigh-stakes industry"},{"time":253886,"text":"that does not practice prior to game time."},{"time":258308,"text":"I want to describe to you a better\napproach through medical simulation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264319,"text":"Well, the first thing we did is we went\nto other high-stakes industries"},{"time":267720,"text":"that had been using this type\nof methodology for decades."},{"time":270614,"text":"This is nuclear power."},{"time":272303,"text":"Nuclear power runs scenarios\non a regular basis"},{"time":276368,"text":"in order to practice\nwhat they hope will never occur."},{"time":280112,"text":"And as we're all very familiar,\nthe airline industry --"},{"time":283984,"text":"we all get on planes now,\ncomforted by the idea"},{"time":287305,"text":"that pilots and crews have trained\non simulators much like these,"},{"time":293125,"text":"training on scenarios\nthat we hope will never occur,"},{"time":295710,"text":"but we know if they did,"},{"time":297914,"text":"they would be prepared for the worst."},{"time":300930,"text":"In fact, the airline industry has gone\nas far as to create fuselages"},{"time":305359,"text":"of simulation environments,"},{"time":306926,"text":"because of the importance\nof the team coming together."},{"time":310813,"text":"This is an evacuation drill simulator."},{"time":313706,"text":"So again, if that ever were to happen,\nthese rare, rare events,"},{"time":317597,"text":"they're ready to act\non the drop of a dime."}]},{"cues":[{"time":322886,"text":"I guess the most compelling for me\nin some ways is the sports industry --"},{"time":328228,"text":"arguably high stakes."},{"time":330473,"text":"You think about a baseball team:\nbaseball players practice."},{"time":333758,"text":"I think it's a beautiful example\nof progressive training."},{"time":336453,"text":"The first thing they do\nis go out to spring training."},{"time":339237,"text":"They go to a spring training camp,"},{"time":341525,"text":"perhaps a simulator in baseball."},{"time":344572,"text":"They're not on the real field,\nbut they're on a simulated field,"},{"time":347638,"text":"and they're playing in the pregame season."},{"time":349695,"text":"Then they make their way to the field\nduring the season games,"},{"time":353216,"text":"and what's the first thing they do\nbefore they start the game?"},{"time":356338,"text":"They go into the batting cage\nand do batting practice for hours,"},{"time":360793,"text":"having different types of pitches\nbeing thrown at them,"},{"time":364148,"text":"hitting ball after ball\nas they limber their muscles,"},{"time":368504,"text":"getting ready for the game itself."},{"time":370501,"text":"And here's the most\nphenomenal part of this,"},{"time":374525,"text":"and for all of you who watch\nany sport event,"},{"time":377049,"text":"you will see this phenomenon happen."},{"time":379841,"text":"The batter gets into the batter's box,"},{"time":382553,"text":"the pitcher gets ready to pitch."},{"time":384698,"text":"Right before the pitch is thrown,"},{"time":387828,"text":"what does that batter do?"},{"time":389061,"text":"The batter steps out of the box"},{"time":392277,"text":"and takes a practice swing."},{"time":394344,"text":"He wouldn't do it any other way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":397392,"text":"I want to talk to you about how\nwe're building practice swings like this"},{"time":400831,"text":"in medicine."},{"time":402010,"text":"We are building batting cages\nfor the patients that we care about"},{"time":406216,"text":"at Boston Children's."},{"time":407468,"text":"I want to use this case\nthat we recently built."},{"time":410484,"text":"It's the case of a four-year-old\nwho had a progressively enlarging head,"},{"time":414779,"text":"and as a result,"},{"time":416080,"text":"had loss of developmental milestones,\nneurologic milestones,"},{"time":419236,"text":"and the reason for this problem is here --"},{"time":422277,"text":"it's called hydrocephalus."}]},{"cues":[{"time":424552,"text":"So, a quick study in neurosurgery."},{"time":427447,"text":"There's the brain,"},{"time":428636,"text":"and you can see the cranium\nsurrounding the brain."},{"time":431649,"text":"What surrounds the brain,\nbetween the brain and cranium,"},{"time":435017,"text":"is something called\ncerebrospinal fluid or fluid,"},{"time":438259,"text":"which acts as a shock absorber."},{"time":440586,"text":"In your heads right now,"},{"time":441932,"text":"there is cerebrospinal fluid\njust bathing your brains"},{"time":445213,"text":"and making its way around."},{"time":447063,"text":"It's produced in one area\nand flows through,"},{"time":449713,"text":"and then is re-exchanged."},{"time":451028,"text":"And this beautiful flow pattern\noccurs for all of us."},{"time":454445,"text":"But unfortunately in some children,"},{"time":456514,"text":"there's a blockage of this flow pattern,"},{"time":459041,"text":"much like a traffic jam."},{"time":461065,"text":"As a result, the fluid accumulates,"},{"time":463912,"text":"and the brain is pushed aside."},{"time":467127,"text":"It has difficulty growing."},{"time":469601,"text":"As a result, the child loses\nneurologic milestones."},{"time":473118,"text":"This is a devastating disease in children."}]},{"cues":[{"time":476973,"text":"The cure for this is surgery."},{"time":480071,"text":"The traditional surgery is to take\na bit of the cranium off,"},{"time":483005,"text":"a bit of the skull,"},{"time":484187,"text":"drain this fluid out,\nstick a drain in place,"},{"time":487154,"text":"and then eventually bring\nthis drain internal to the body."},{"time":489906,"text":"Big operation."},{"time":492096,"text":"But some great news is that advances\nin neurosurgical care"},{"time":496437,"text":"have allowed us to develop\nminimally invasive approaches"},{"time":500170,"text":"to this surgery."},{"time":501354,"text":"Through a small pinhole,\na camera can be inserted,"},{"time":506932,"text":"led into the deep brain structure,"},{"time":509684,"text":"and cause a little hole in a membrane\nthat allows all that fluid to drain,"},{"time":513661,"text":"much like it would in a sink."},{"time":515733,"text":"All of a sudden, the brain\nis no longer under pressure,"},{"time":518872,"text":"can re-expand"},{"time":520353,"text":"and we cure the child\nthrough a single-hole incision."}]},{"cues":[{"time":524658,"text":"But here's the problem:"},{"time":526097,"text":"hydrocephalus is relatively rare."},{"time":528910,"text":"And there are no good training methods"},{"time":531344,"text":"to get really good at getting\nthis scope to the right place."},{"time":534992,"text":"But surgeons have been quite creative\nabout this, even our own."},{"time":539330,"text":"And they've come up with training models."},{"time":541362,"text":"Here's the current training model."}]},{"cues":[{"time":543111,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":545093,"text":"I kid you not."},{"time":546774,"text":"This is a red pepper,\nnot made in Hollywood;"},{"time":549237,"text":"it's real red pepper."},{"time":551000,"text":"And what surgeons do is they stick\na scope into the pepper,"},{"time":553971,"text":"and they do what is called a \"seedectomy.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":557093,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":558884,"text":"They use this scope to remove seeds\nusing a little tweezer."},{"time":565812,"text":"And that is a way to get under their belts"},{"time":568464,"text":"the rudimentary components\nof doing this surgery."},{"time":572116,"text":"Then they head right into\nthe apprenticeship model,"},{"time":574576,"text":"seeing many of them\nas they present themselves,"},{"time":577472,"text":"then doing it, and then teaching it --"},{"time":579759,"text":"waiting for these patients to arrive."},{"time":582527,"text":"We can do a lot better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":584090,"text":"We are manufacturing\nreproductions of children"},{"time":588841,"text":"in order for surgeons and surgical\nteams to rehearse"},{"time":592771,"text":"in the most relevant possible ways."},{"time":595175,"text":"Let me show you this."},{"time":597146,"text":"Here's my team"},{"time":598678,"text":"in what's called the SIM Engineering\nDivision of the Simulator Program."},{"time":603320,"text":"This is an amazing team of individuals."},{"time":606187,"text":"They are mechanical engineers;"},{"time":608486,"text":"you're seeing here, illustrators."},{"time":610935,"text":"They take primary data\nfrom CT scans and MRIs,"},{"time":615531,"text":"translate it into digital information,"},{"time":618885,"text":"animate it,"},{"time":620215,"text":"put it together into the components\nof the child itself,"},{"time":625030,"text":"surface-scan elements of the child\nthat have been casted as needed,"},{"time":628848,"text":"depending on the surgery itself,"},{"time":631457,"text":"and then take this digital data\nand be able to output it"},{"time":635372,"text":"on state-of-the-art,\nthree-dimensional printing devices"},{"time":639144,"text":"that allow us to print the components"},{"time":641438,"text":"exactly to the micron detail of what\nthe child's anatomy will look like."},{"time":647130,"text":"You can see here,"},{"time":648458,"text":"the skull of this child being printed"},{"time":650916,"text":"in the hours before\nwe performed this surgery."}]},{"cues":[{"time":654618,"text":"But we could not do this work"},{"time":657218,"text":"without our dear friends on the West Coast\nin Hollywood, California."},{"time":662780,"text":"These are individuals\nthat are incredibly talented"},{"time":666034,"text":"at being able to recreate reality."},{"time":668482,"text":"It was not a long leap for us."},{"time":672930,"text":"The more we got into this field,"},{"time":674530,"text":"the more it became clear to us\nthat we are doing cinematography."},{"time":678990,"text":"We're doing filmmaking,"},{"time":680891,"text":"it's just that the actors are not actors."},{"time":683909,"text":"They're real doctors and nurses."},{"time":687190,"text":"So these are some photos\nof our dear friends at Fractured FX"},{"time":690593,"text":"in Hollywood California,"},{"time":692086,"text":"an Emmy-Award-winning\nspecial effects firm."},{"time":695684,"text":"This is Justin Raleigh and his group --"},{"time":698878,"text":"this is not one of our patients --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":700550,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":701932,"text":"but kind of the exquisite work\nthat these individuals do."},{"time":705024,"text":"We have now collaborated\nand fused our experience,"},{"time":708652,"text":"bringing their group\nto Boston Children's Hospital,"},{"time":711082,"text":"sending our group\nout to Hollywood, California"},{"time":713762,"text":"and exchanging around this"},{"time":715155,"text":"to be able to develop\nthese type of simulators."}]},{"cues":[{"time":718182,"text":"What I'm about to show you\nis a reproduction of this child."},{"time":727172,"text":"You'll notice here that every hair\non the child's head is reproduced."},{"time":732324,"text":"And in fact, this is also\nthat reproduced child --"},{"time":736051,"text":"and I apologize for any queasy stomachs,"},{"time":739268,"text":"but that is a reproduction and simulation"},{"time":742152,"text":"of the child they're about to operate on."},{"time":746493,"text":"Here's that membrane we had talked about,"},{"time":748955,"text":"the inside of this child's brain."},{"time":751538,"text":"What you're going to be seeing here\nis, on one side, the actual patient,"},{"time":756530,"text":"and on the other side, the simulator."},{"time":758833,"text":"As I mentioned, a scope, a little camera,\nneeds to make its way down,"},{"time":763207,"text":"and you're seeing that here."},{"time":764632,"text":"It needs to make a small hole\nin this membrane"},{"time":766980,"text":"and allow this fluid to seep out."},{"time":771155,"text":"I won't do a quiz show to see\nwho thinks which side is which,"},{"time":776962,"text":"but on the right is the simulator."}]},{"cues":[{"time":780683,"text":"So surgeons can now produce\ntraining opportunities,"},{"time":784505,"text":"do these surgeries\nas many times as they want,"},{"time":787582,"text":"to their heart's content,\nuntil they feel comfortable."},{"time":790448,"text":"And then, and only then,\nbring the child into the operating room."},{"time":794037,"text":"But we don't stop here."},{"time":795230,"text":"We know that a key step to this\nis not just the skill itself,"},{"time":799564,"text":"but combining that skill with a team\nwho's going to deliver that care."}]},{"cues":[{"time":804119,"text":"Now we turn to Formula One."},{"time":807025,"text":"And here is an example\nof a technician putting on a tire"},{"time":810299,"text":"and doing that time and time\nagain on this car."},{"time":813532,"text":"But that is very quickly\ngoing to be incorporated"},{"time":816541,"text":"within team-training experiences,"},{"time":818496,"text":"now as a full team orchestrating\nthe exchange of tires"},{"time":822729,"text":"and getting this car back on the speedway."},{"time":826274,"text":"We've done that step in health care,"},{"time":829575,"text":"so now what you're about to see\nis a simulated operation."},{"time":834760,"text":"We've taken the simulator\nI just described to you,"},{"time":837171,"text":"we've brought it into the operating room\nat Boston Children's Hospital,"},{"time":840596,"text":"and these individuals --\nthese native teams, operative teams --"},{"time":844275,"text":"are doing the surgery before the surgery."},{"time":847822,"text":"Operate twice;"},{"time":849583,"text":"cut once."},{"time":851119,"text":"Let me show that to you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":853417,"text":"(Video) Surgical team member 1:\nYou want the head down or head up?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":856554,"text":"STM 2: Can you lower it down to 10?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":858282,"text":"STM 3: And then lower\nthe whole table down a little bit?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":860955,"text":"STM 4: Table coming down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":864856,"text":"STM 3: All right, this\nis behaving like a vessel."},{"time":867585,"text":"Could we have the scissors back, please?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":869696,"text":"STM 5: I'm taking my gloves,\n8 to 8 1/2, all right? I'll be right in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":873021,"text":"STM 6: Great! Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":876336,"text":"Peter Weinstock: It's really amazing."},{"time":878193,"text":"The second step to this,\nwhich is critical,"},{"time":880309,"text":"is we take these teams out\nimmediately and debrief them."},{"time":883432,"text":"We use the same technologies"},{"time":884920,"text":"that are used in Lean\nand Six Sigma in the military,"},{"time":889632,"text":"and we bring them out\nand talk about what went right,"},{"time":892741,"text":"but more importantly,"},{"time":894410,"text":"we talk about what didn't go well,"},{"time":896901,"text":"and how we're going to fix it."},{"time":898860,"text":"Then we bring them right back in\nand do it again."},{"time":901638,"text":"Deliberative batting practice\nin the moments when it matters most."}]},{"cues":[{"time":908438,"text":"Let's go back to this case now."},{"time":911083,"text":"Same child,"},{"time":912484,"text":"but now let me describe\nhow we care for this child"},{"time":914898,"text":"at Boston Children's Hospital."},{"time":916385,"text":"This child was born\nat three o'clock in the morning."},{"time":918895,"text":"At two o'clock in the morning,"},{"time":920926,"text":"we assembled the team,"},{"time":923076,"text":"and took the reproduced anatomy"},{"time":924901,"text":"that we would gain\nout of scans and images,"},{"time":928630,"text":"and brought that team\nto the virtual bedside,"},{"time":931420,"text":"to a simulated bedside --"},{"time":933031,"text":"the same team that's going to operate\non this child in the hours ahead --"},{"time":936596,"text":"and we have them do the procedure."},{"time":939591,"text":"Let me show you a moment of this."},{"time":942212,"text":"This is not a real incision."},{"time":945451,"text":"And the baby has not yet been born."},{"time":949113,"text":"Imagine this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":952133,"text":"So now the conversations\nthat I have with families"},{"time":956045,"text":"in the intensive care unit\nat Boston Children's Hospital"},{"time":958769,"text":"are totally different."},{"time":960762,"text":"Imagine this conversation:"},{"time":963649,"text":"\"Not only do we take care of this disorder\nfrequently in our ICU,"},{"time":968524,"text":"and not only have we done surgeries"},{"time":970726,"text":"like the surgery we're going\nto do on your child,"},{"time":973185,"text":"but we have done your child's surgery."},{"time":977956,"text":"And we did it two hours ago."},{"time":980510,"text":"And we did it 10 times."},{"time":983266,"text":"And now we're prepared to take them\nback to the operating room.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":988731,"text":"So a new technology in health care:"},{"time":992167,"text":"lifelike rehearsal."},{"time":995059,"text":"Practicing prior to game time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":999632,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1000836,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}